{"word":"Booth","slug":"booth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Booth</b> Made of boughs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=4&verse=5'>Jon 4:5</a><br/> Made for cattle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=17'>Gen 33:17</a><br/> Made for watchmen<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=27&verse=18'>Job 27:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=8'>Isa 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=24&verse=20'>Isa 24:20</a><br/> Prescribed for the Israelites to dwell in, during the Feast of Tabernacles, to celebrate their wanderings in the wilderness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=43'>Lev 23:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=16'>Neh 8:16</a>"}]}